itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway go through their UFC over/unders on mybookie.com/drinkinbros and welcome John Brenkus to discuss the UFC 250 event showcasing female fighters such as Felecia Spencer and Amanda Nunes and other fighters such as Raphael Assuncao and Cody Garbrandt, and the three look forward to the 2020 Stanley Cup playoffs and start of the NBA season.
